      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "lineHeight": 1.4,
      "text": "MeterReadingsConsumer (BackgroundService)\nConsumeUntilCancelledAsync: reconnect loop (5s delay)\nHandleMessageAsync:\n  Deserialize JSON → MeterReadingMessage\n  BasicAck on success\n  BasicNack requeue=false → dead-letter (bad JSON)\n  BasicNack requeue=true → retry (other errors)",
      "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "rect_5",
      "originalText": "MeterReadingsConsumer (BackgroundService)\nConsumeUntilCancelledAsync: reconnect loop (5s delay)\nHandleMessageAsync:\n  Deserialize JSON → MeterReadingMessage\n  BasicAck on success\n  BasicNack requeue=false → dead-letter (bad JSON)\n  BasicNack requeue=true → retry (other errors)"
    },

