      "x": 210, "y": 1110, "width": 380, "height": 200,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e2e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null,
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "lineHeight": 1.4,
      "text": "ProcessReadingsCommand → MediatR\nProcessReadingsCommandHandler\n─────────────────────────────────\n1. GetOrCreateMeterWithCacheAsync:\n   Redis.GetMeterIdAsync → DB fallback if null\n   Redis.SetMeterIdAsync after DB hit\n2. Per reading:\n   IsReadingCachedAsync (Redis) → skip if hit\n   InsertReadingAsync (DB, ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING)\n   MarkReadingProcessedAsync (Redis)",
      "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "rect_6",
      "originalText": "ProcessReadingsCommand → MediatR\nProcessReadingsCommandHandler\n─────────────────────────────────\n1. GetOrCreateMeterWithCacheAsync:\n   Redis.GetMeterIdAsync → DB fallback if null\n   Redis.SetMeterIdAsync after DB hit\n2. Per reading:\n   IsReadingCachedAsync (Redis) → skip if hit\n   InsertReadingAsync (DB, ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING)\n   MarkReadingProcessedAsync (Redis)"
    },

    {
      "id": "rect_7", "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 680, "y": 1100, "width": 360, "height": 300,
